        <section id="cameras">
            <h2>Cameras</h2>
            <p>Our network of cameras provides real-time video feeds to monitor traffic conditions. These cameras help in identifying congestion and accidents.</p>
        </section>

        <section id="sensors">
            <h2>Sensors</h2>
            <p>Various sensors are deployed on roads to collect data on vehicle counts, speeds, and types. This data is crucial for traffic management and planning.</p>
        </section>

        <section id="gps">
            <h2>GPS Data</h2>
            <p>GPS data from vehicles allows us to track their locations and movements in real-time, providing insights into traffic flow and patterns.</p>
        </section>

        <section id="mobile-apps">
            <h2>Mobile Applications</h2>
            <p>Mobile applications enable users to report traffic conditions and receive updates on road status, helping to improve overall traffic management.</p>
        </section>
           <section id="public-transport">
            <h2>Promoting Public Transport</h2>
            <p>Public transport is a sustainable and efficient way to travel. Here are some options:</p>

            <div class="transport-option">
                <h3>Buses</h3>
                <p>Buses provide an affordable and flexible means of transportation, connecting various parts of the city and reducing traffic congestion.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="transport-option">
                <h3>Trains</h3>
                <p>Trains offer a fast and reliable way to travel longer distances, minimizing travel time and environmental impact.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="transport-option">
                <h3>Bike Sharing</h3>
                <p>Bike-sharing programs encourage eco-friendly travel and provide a convenient way to navigate urban areas while promoting health and fitness.</p>
            </div>
        </section>
           <section id="real-time-updates">
            <h2>Real-Time Updates</h2>
            <p>Stay informed with live tracking of public transport schedules and delays through our mobile apps and web platforms. Here’s what you can expect:</p>

            <div class="update-option">
                <h3>Live Tracking</h3>
                <p>Track the real-time location of buses and trains on your device, ensuring you never miss your ride.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="update-option">
                <h3>Schedule Updates</h3>
                <p>Receive instant notifications about schedule changes, helping you plan your journey more effectively.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="update-option">
                <h3>Delay Notifications</h3>
                <p>Get alerts for any delays or disruptions in service, allowing you to adjust your travel plans accordingly.</p>
            </div>
        </section>
          <section id="bike-lanes"
            <h2>Bike Lanes</h2>
            <p>Dedicated bike lanes are essential for ensuring the safety of cyclists. They provide a clear path for cyclists, separate from motor vehicle traffic, encouraging more people to choose cycling as a mode of transport.</p>
        </section>

        <section id="bike-sharing">
            <h2>Bike Sharing Program</h2>
            <p>Our bike-sharing program allows users to rent bikes for short trips, making cycling accessible to everyone. With numerous stations across the city, it's easy to pick up and drop off bikes at convenient locations.</p>
        </section>

        <section id="parking-facilities">
            <h2>Parking Facilities</h2>
            <p>We provide secure parking facilities for bicycles at key locations throughout the city. These facilities are equipped with bike racks and lockers, ensuring that cyclists have a safe place to store their bikes while they go about their day.</p>
        </section>

        <section id="incentives">
            <h2>Incentives for Users</h2>
            <p>We collaborate with local governments to create incentive programs that reward frequent cyclists. Here’s how:</p>
            <div class="incentive-option">
                <h3>Discounts on Bike Rentals</h3>
                <p>Frequent users of the bike-sharing program can receive discounts on their next rentals, encouraging more cycling.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="incentive-option">
                <h3>Rewards for Cycling</h3>
                <p>Users can earn points for every trip they take, which can be redeemed for rewards such as free rentals or merchandise.</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="real-time-updates">
            <h2>Real-Time Updates</h2>
            <p>Stay informed with live tracking of bike availability and parking space through our mobile apps and web platforms. Here’s what you can expect:</p>
            <div class="update-option">
                <h3>Live Bike Availability</h3>
                <p>Check the availability of bikes at nearby stations in real-time, ensuring you can find a bike when you need it.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="update-option">
                <h3>Parking Space Updates</h3>
                <p>Get notifications about available parking spaces for bikes, making it easier to plan your trips.</p>
            </div>
        </section>
         <section id="charging-stations">
            <h2>Access to Charging Stations</h2>
            <p>We provide easy access to electronic vehicle charging stations across the city. Our platform maps the locations of these stations, making it convenient for EV users to find charging points nearby.</p>
        </section>

        <section id="real-time-updates">
            <h2>Real-Time Availability Updates</h2>
            <p>Stay informed with real-time updates on the availability of charging stations. Our app provides live data on which stations are currently in use and which are available, helping you plan your charging stops effectively.</p>
            <div class="update-option">
                <h3>Live Station Status</h3>
                <p>Check the status of charging stations in real-time to avoid waiting times and ensure a smooth charging experience.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="update-option">
                <h3>Map Integration</h3>
                <p>Our interactive map allows you to view all charging stations in your vicinity, complete with availability status and user ratings.</p>
            </div>
        </section>

