            <section id="awareness-campaigns">
            <h2>User Engagement and Awareness Campaigns</h2>
            <p>We are launching various awareness campaigns to educate the public about the benefits of using public transport and eco-friendly alternatives. Join us in spreading the word!</p>
            <div class="campaign-option">
                <h3>Social Media Campaigns</h3>
                <p>Follow us on social media to participate in our campaigns, share your experiences, and learn more about sustainable travel options.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="campaign-option">
                <h3>Community Events</h3>
                <p>Join our community events where we discuss the importance of public transport and eco-friendly travel. Engage with local leaders and fellow citizens.</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="benefits">
            <h2>Benefits of Using Public Transport</h2>
            <p>Public transport offers numerous benefits, including:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Reduced traffic congestion</li>
                <li>Lower carbon emissions</li>
                <li>Cost savings on fuel and parking</li>
                <li>Increased accessibility to various parts of the city</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section id="eco-friendly-options">
            <h2>Eco-Friendly Alternatives</h2>
            <p>In addition to public transport, consider these eco-friendly alternatives:</p>
            <div class="alternative-option">
                <h3>Cycling</h3>
                <p>Cycling is a healthy and environmentally friendly way to travel short distances. Join local bike-sharing programs to make cycling more accessible.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="alternative-option">
                <h3>Walking</h3>
                <p>For short trips, walking is the best option. It reduces emissions and promotes a healthier lifestyle.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="alternative-option">
                <h3>Carpooling</h3>
                <p>Carpooling with friends or colleagues can significantly reduce the number of vehicles on the road, leading to lower emissions and cost savings.</p>
            </div>
